og/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eec8ab0ab6aa43846a85d15dc6855bab429f23f","tid":2232741,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"暖水袋敷下個肚"},{"pid":"d2249b41f4071ad2079424329929c03ceff48931","tid":2232741,"uid":238883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"米水<br />\n<br />\n你當半個量杯米，加5，6杯水煮<br />\n開頭大火<br />\n滾起後轉中小火， 總之唔好滾到啲水飛晒出黎<br />\n個啲米水就係幫到你止瀉嘅米水<br />\n米必須熟透， 等閒要用 湯羹或快子， 了2下以免痴底<br />\n<br />\n當你見到啲水變白色<br />\n有小小杰杰地， 有啲膠膠地， 但唔係粥呀<br />\n咁你可以筆啲水出黎， 攤凍少少就飲得<br />\n有淨就留係煲內<br />\n下次再翻滾佢， 加返小小水， 都係中細火<br />\n<br />\n多水好過少水， 因為你要飲嘅係水， 米唔食<br />\n一粒都唔食<br />\n<br />\n臨瞓前咩都唔好食"},{"pid":"65a4173f07f16244cced32373fd2b95b7743fce6","tid":2232741,"uid":84751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"3次唔算多<br />\n但可以試下沖暖水涼暖下個肚<br />\n咪食止痾藥, 食完聽日都係爛屎同會係咁放臭屁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7385f780c80b0d5e8b2e0e99f0b03a87951608","tid":2232741,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"放粒dulcolax 以毒攻毒啦"},{"pid":"7ae7c6cbae4854c47b494f4cf1857bfaf32676cc","tid":2232741,"uid":6374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"琴日返工肚痛到收工痾左2次<br />\n到夜晚痾左4次 訓覺痾左5次<br />\n今日痾左2次<br />\n現家痾緊第1次<br />\nTotal14次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfb92fe164d6ef8061657a47f48b1c5467cd2e6","tid":2232741,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"喇叭牌正露丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理政見<br />\n佢真係幾勁"},{"pid":"278d8916bab0d660b995244efb25f179b190e8af","tid":2232741